- Use caching for expensive operations, especially LLM calls
- Consider pagination for large datasets or responses
- Optimize prompt sizes to reduce token usage
- Use async patterns for I/O-bound operations where appropriate
- Profile and optimize code paths that handle large files
- Implement appropriate timeouts for external API calls
- Consider memory usage when processing large datasets
